#: ../../content/applications/hr/fleet.rst:7
msgid "Fleet"
msgstr "Flota"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/fleet.rst:9
msgid ""
"Odoo *Fleet* organizes all the vehicles, contracts, and repairs of all the "
"vehicles."
